=== 可能的第二顆行星 ===<!-- this section is linked from redirect "[[Gliese_436_c|Gliese 436 c]]"-->
在2008年，聲稱發現了第二顆行星，命名為"格利澤436c"，軌道週期為5.2天，軌道半長軸是0.045天文單位<ref>{{cite journal | author = Ribas, I.; Font-Ribera, S. and Beaulieu, J. P. | title = A ~5 M<sub>⊙</sub> Super-Earth Orbiting GJ 436?: The Power of Near-Grazing Transits | year = 2008 | journal = [[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume = 677 | issue = 1 | pages = L59–L62 | doi = 10.1086/587961 | bibcode = 2008ApJ...677L..59R}}</ref>，這顆行星的質量大約是5[[地球質量|地球質量]]，半徑大約大於1.5地球半徑<ref name="reuters"/>。儘管在媒體上宣稱這是已知質量最小的行星，但它仍然比1992年發現，環繞著脈衝星[[PSR_B1257+12|PSR B1257+12]]的三顆行星的質量還要大。而以其大小，這顆行星被認為是岩石的[[類地行星|類地行星]] <ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.space.com/scienceastronomy/080409-smallest-exoplanet.html | title=New Super-Earth is Smallest Yet | work=Space.com | accessdate=2008-04-10 | archive-date=2010-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030081226/http://www.space.com/scienceastronomy/080409-smallest-exoplanet.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。西班牙的科學家在2008年4月宣稱分析過格利澤436c對格利澤436b軌道的影響<ref name="reuters">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUSL0956988620080409 |title=Reuters |access-date=2011-04-11 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202103222/https://www.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUSL0956988620080409 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在該系統最大可能配置規則的情形下，進一步的分析顯示內側行星凌的長度沒有改變。此外，如果這些軌道參數是正確的，這個系統在UA的[http://www.lpl.arizona.edu/~rory/research/xsp/dynamics/ Extrasolar Planet Interactions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lpl.arizona.edu/~rory/research/xsp/dynamics/ |date=20160505160348 }}圖表上只有不穩定的軌道。因此，認為"格利澤436c"不太可能存在<ref>{{cite journal | author = Alonso, R. ''et al.'' | title = Limits to the planet candidate GJ 436c | year = 2008 | journal = [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | volume = 487 | issue = 1 | pages = L5–L8 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:200810007 | bibcode = 2008A&A...487L...5A}}</ref>，並且此一發現在2008年波士頓舉行的行星凌日會議中被撤銷<ref>{{cite web | url = http://exoplanet.eu/star.php?st=GJ+436 | title = Notes for star GJ 436 | work = The Extrasolar Planets Encyclopaedia | author = Schneider, J. | accessdate = 2008-09-07 | archive-date = 2012-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120524045725/http://exoplanet.eu/star.php?st=GJ+436 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

儘管撤回了，但研究指出還是存在著有其它行星環繞著格利澤436的可能性<ref>{{cite journal|author=Bean, J. L. and Seifahrt, A.|title=Observational Consequences of the Recently Proposed Super-Earth Orbiting GJ436|year=2008|journal=[[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]]|volume=487|issue=2|pages=L25–L28|doi=10.1051/0004-6361:200810278|bibcode=2008A&A...487L..25B}}</ref>。借助在2005年1月11日在NMSU上自動紀錄的一次，被業餘天文學家觀測到，但被忽略的凌日事件，認為格利澤436b的軌道傾角有增加的趨勢，僅管這一趨勢仍未獲得證實。 但這種趨勢與一顆質量少於12地球質量，軌道半徑在0.08AU以內的行星軌道是相容的<ref name=coughlin>{{cite journal|author=Coughlin, J. L. ''et al.''|title=New Observations and a Possible Detection of Parameter Variations in the Transits of Gliese 436b|year=2008|journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]]|volume=689|issue=2|pages=L149–L152|doi=10.1086/595822|bibcode=2008ApJ...689L.149C}}</ref>。這也仍然未被證實<ref name="hubble">{{cite journal
